===市民健康===
圖文巴當地有一所公立醫院－Toowoomba Base Hospital，以及兩所私立醫院：聖安德魯圖文巴醫院（St. Andrew's Toowoomba Hospital）、聖文森醫院（St. Vincents Hospital）。圖文巴曾為澳大利亞國內自殺率最高的地區<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wesleymission.org.au/releases/November05/051108a.asp |title=LifeForce brings suicide prevention message to Toowoomba |accessdate=2008-10-22 |archive-date=2008-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080728085750/http://www.wesleymission.org.au/releases/November05/051108a.asp |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

